title: 3 Bed 2 Bath Apartment Available Early October!
posting_body: ['_______________________________________', 'ABOUT THE COMMUNITY:', '________________________________________', 'Enjoy the best Plymouth has to offer at Shenandoah Woods.', "Located near Parker's Lake, Shenandoah Woods offers spacious apartments with private balconies or walk-out patios.", 'Our community features beautiful views of surrounding parks and wetlands, in addition to onsite laundry, play area, elevator, BBQ area, and party room.', '1 heated underground parking space is included in your rent.', 'Shenandoah Woods is conveniently located near Highway 55 and Vicksburg Lane, just minutes away from everything you need.', '________________________________________', 'UNIT & COMMUNITY FEATURES:', '________________________________________', '❖ Heat included in rent!', '❖ Air conditioning', '❖ Dishwashers', '❖ Section 8 Vouchers Accepted.', '❖ Heated Underground Parking', '❖ Controlled Access', '❖ Elevator', '❖ On-site Laundry', '❖ Onsite Management', '❖ BBQ area', '❖ Community room', '❖ Playground', '❖ Wayzata School District', 'All applications are available in the office.', 'Application Fee: $45 per adult', 'Pre-Lease Deposit: $200 (Refundable if not approved)', 'Security Deposit: One month rent', 'Lease Duration: 12 months.', '*Photos are from similar apartments in the building, not necessarily current ones listed for rent.*', 'Some of our apartments do have income and student restrictions that need to be followed in addition to our standard screening policies.', 'Contact', 'show contact info', 'for more information.']
